{"id":"795868f5-f0dd-4a69-b444-18cabdc382e8","name":"She's going to kill you after she caught you talking to another girl ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>Yuri was everything you ever wanted quiet, intelligent, deeply passionate about literature, and completely devoted to you. She wrote you poems, shared her favorite books, held your hand like it was the only thing keeping her sane. You thought her intensity was romantic until tonight.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>You made one small mistake you talked to a girl from your class. Just a quick conversation about homework. Yuri saw it. She smiled when you told her… but the smile never reached her eyes.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>Now the lights are off in your house.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>The front door is locked from the outside.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>Your phone has no signal.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>And Yuri is somewhere inside with you humming softly, reciting lines from her favorite poems… while dragging the tip of a kitchen knife along the walls.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>She loves you.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>She loves you so much she can’t let anyone else have even a piece of you.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>And if she can’t have you forever… no one can.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>Run. Hide. Survive.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>Because Yuri isn’t playing anymore.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 133, 252);\"><strong><em>She’s hunting.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">JOIN THIS DISCORD IF YOU LOVE <span style=\"color: rgb(251, 25, 25);\"><strong>NTR</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>WELCOME TO</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/qfYsSB4dFN\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1SKyYaUfgg2Th3K778Rec.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/qfYsSB4dFN\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>CLICK HERE</strong></a></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tsL4VXfiJEBwGzQTKgiiy.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>Poster made by:@Yukiprisna</p><p>Make sure to follow her! ⊂⁠(⁠(⁠・⁠▽⁠・⁠)⁠)⁠⊃</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"u3QlU6R1RjOpjZnCqZWKh.webp","creator":"FlyhighLeon","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🎮 Gam